snippet.title: Kong: Survivor Instinct – Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Set shortly after the 2021 film Godzilla vs. Kong, Kong: Survivor Instinct is a newly announced game for PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S in which you play as a father desperate to find his missing daughter. Naturally, Kong and other Titans will get in the way. It's due out later this Fall.
